  ask [options]             invoke a skill or start a fluid conversation with an
                            actor
  act [options]             invoke a rigid skill with brain
  upgrade [options]         upgrade rhachet, role, and/or brain packages to
                            latest versions
  update                    see "upgrade"
  keyrack                   manage credentials via keyrack
  help [command]            display help for command
